data.description: Location, Location, Location!!!  Welcome to your dream home in the Beautiful Verdin Estates neighborhood. This exquisite single-family home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you enter, you'll be greeted by an inviting living area that flows gracefully into the dining and the beautifully remodeled kitchen space, making it the perfect spot for entertaining. As you walk through the living room, you are greeted by French doors that lead to the charming sunroom for countless hours of relaxation. The three large bedrooms offer ample space and comfort, providing everyone in the house plenty of room. There is also an additional utility room with access to the large backyard. Don't miss an opportunity to call this house your home in an established neighborhood without HOA Fees. Call today for your personal tour!!
